Solution:
_________
- need to add the result paramenter in action.- means whetever updated values to the return- immediately.

action UpdateStatus parameter zstatus_Str  result[1] $self;
here:
$self - it represents the current entity. means which entity return   the results.

class- changes-lhc_zr_dbt_trav
__________________
  methods : updatestatus for modify 
            importing keys for action R_DBT_TRAV~UpdateStatus  result result. <-- add the result parameter in method interface

Class implementations: after changing we got the ne value right.. in updatestatus method implementation.:
________________
  1. modify enitties --> update the data to DB- ZR_DBT_TRAV
  2. after update the data - we have to immediately read the data using read enitities.
  3. if you read selected entity, you will get the update value- whatever you are getting - you have to pass through that result parameter.

  Dynamic value you to get : keys

  read entities of zr_dbt_trav in local mode enitity r_dbt_Trav 
  all fields with corresponding #( keys ) data( result ). --> once get the data -- i am move it into the result parameter- defined in interface.

  result = lt_Result.( send key data in %tky )

  Ex: 
  class lhc_zr_dbt_trav definition inheriting from CL_ABAP_BEHAVIOR_HANDLER.
    private section.
      methods : update status for modify 
                importing keys for action R_DBT_TRAV~updatestatus rsult reult.
  endclass.

  class lhc_zr_dbt_trav implementation.
    method updatestatus.
        // records updated in db.
        modify entities of zr_dbt_trav in local mode entity r_dbt_trav
        update fields ( Status )
        with value #( for key in keys ( %key-TravelId = Key-TravelId
                                        status = key-%param-status ) ) 
        reported data( lt_reported )
        failed data( lt_failed ).

        // once updated- again read those records and send to the output.
        read entities of zr_dbt_trav in local mode enitity r_dbt_Trav 
        all fields with corresponding #( keys ) data( result ). 

        result = value #( for ls_result in lt_Result( %tky = ls_result-%tky
                                                      %param = ls_result ).

    endmethod.
  endclass.

